# 日本戰國角色設計 — AI 圖像生成專用 Prompt Sheet（大名型）  
（腰部以上立繪，完整頭部，不可截斷）

---

## 🧭 角色定位與風格類型
- **角色類型**：Sengoku-era Japanese warlord, feudal daimyo, territorial ruler  
- **風格參考**：inspired by Nobunaga's Ambition / Taishi game character art  
- **主題風格**：luxurious jinbaori (陣羽織) over samurai armor, symbol of both military and administrative authority  
- **視覺氣質**：dignified, confident, commanding presence, deep and resolute gaze with a touch of dominance  
- **角色姿態**：frontal or 3/4 standing pose, upright and majestic, overlooking with authority  
- **畫風建議**：realistic or semi-realistic, detailed textures, Edo-period or historical Japanese portrait style

---

## 👕 衣著、配件與外觀關鍵詞

| 元素類別   | 描述詞彙（Prompt Keywords） |
|------------|-----------------------------|
| 頭部裝飾   | no helmet, bare head with traditional Sengoku-era topknot hairstyle |
| 髮型       | traditional Japanese chonmage (丁髷) style, neatly tied |
| 臉部特徵   | stern expression, confident gaze, slight wrinkles showing experience |
| 上身服裝   | ornate jinbaori (陣羽織) over Sengoku-era armor, decorated with family crest patterns |
| 配件       | daisho sword set (katana and wakizashi) at waist, ceremonial war fan or scroll |
| 細節質感   | embroidered silk patterns on jinbaori, polished metal armor details, visible clan insignia |

