## 🌄 背景與構圖建議
- **背景顏色**：castle interior, blurred battlefield, or golden sunset glow  
- **構圖形式**：frontal or 3/4 view, **waist-up** portrait, full head visible  
- **燈光質感**：dramatic but balanced lighting to emphasize jinbaori and facial features  
- **肌理細節**：clear embroidery texture, fabric folds, facial shadow depth showing leadership aura

